thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Steven & Helen Laios

author: Steven & Helen Laios
title: Steven & Helen Laios
text: Michelle, Thomas and Portia are honest, trustworthy easy to deal with and very knowledgeable with real estate. The auction of our house was an outstanding success. We felt comfortable that they had our best interests at heart. I would highly recommend them!
